Package: tabular
Title: TFL Rendering for Regulatory Submissions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam", email = "about.vignesh@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Native emission of clinical submission tables to RTF,
    LaTeX, HTML, PDF, and DOCX. Handles decimal alignment via font
    metrics, multi-level column headers with passthrough leaves,
    predicate-targeted styling, and group-aware pagination. Designed
    for CDISC ADaM workflows and FDA / EMA / PMDA regulatory
    submissions.
